<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:12:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>10月7日之后，以色列城市变成鬼城还有希望吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/is-there-hope-for-israeli-city-turned-ghost-town-after-october-7/0000018d-0741-dd94-a9cd-47ed08780000</link><description>位于以色列与加沙地带边境的斯德洛特是 10 月 7 日受灾最严重的城市。市长阿隆·戴维迪现在表示：“如果一百万加沙人返回加沙地带北部，那就是一次失败”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 11:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/is-there-hope-for-israeli-city-turned-ghost-town-after-october-7/0000018d-0741-dd94-a9cd-47ed08780000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯公布三名以色列人在加沙被扣为人质的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/hamas-releases-video-of-three-israelis-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018d-0c29-d71c-ad9f-4fab2b520000</link><description>视频发布后不久，美国总统乔·拜登发表声明，纪念加沙人质被关押100天：“我再次向所有人质及其家人重申我的承诺——我们与你们同在”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 10:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/hamas-releases-video-of-three-israelis-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018d-0c29-d71c-ad9f-4fab2b520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列足球运动员被土耳其当局释放，预计将返回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/israeli-soccer-player-arrested-in-turkey-for-celebrating-goal-with-tribute-to-hostages/0000018d-0c0f-d71c-ad9f-4f8f416e0000</link><description>萨吉夫·耶赫兹克尔 (Sagiv Yehezkhel) 在庆祝进球并向在加沙被扣为人质的以色列人致敬后被拘留审讯</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/israeli-soccer-player-arrested-in-turkey-for-celebrating-goal-with-tribute-to-hostages/0000018d-0c0f-d71c-ad9f-4f8f416e0000</guid></item><item><title>释放人质的代价是以色列政府承认失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/the-price-of-freeing-hostages-admitting-the-war-has-failed/0000018d-0958-d71c-ad9f-4bdaac800000</link><description>在新一轮人质协议谈判中，哈马斯的要求似乎比上一次协议高出几乎无法估量。 ■ 同意这些要求将意味着结束与以色列的战争，而以色列未能实现击败哈马斯并削弱其能力的目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 04:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/the-price-of-freeing-hostages-admitting-the-war-has-failed/0000018d-0958-d71c-ad9f-4bdaac800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部城市拉阿纳纳发生冲撞和刺伤袭击，造成人员伤亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-live/hamas-releases-video-of-three-israeli-hostages/0000018d-0af5-d71c-ad9f-4bf75d0b0000</link><description>辛贝特揭露伊朗招募和动员以色列公民的网络 ■ 因在比赛期间向加沙扣押的人质致敬而在土耳其被捕的以色列足球运动员将被释放给以色列 ■ 哈马斯发布 3 名以色列人质的新视频后，美国政府重申致力于确保安全释放所有人质 ■ 以色列国防军表示，自加沙地面行动开始以来，已有 188 名士兵在战斗中丧生，并宣布加沙南部有一名士兵死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:23:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-live/hamas-releases-video-of-three-israeli-hostages/0000018d-0af5-d71c-ad9f-4bf75d0b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的精神卫生预算将被削减，而不是20亿谢克尔的补助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-a-two-billion-shekel-supplement-israels-mental-health-budget-will-be-cut/0000018d-0a96-d71c-ad9f-4b963c6a0000</link><description>2024年国家预算将卫生部预算削减4亿谢克尔，而就在几周前，卫生部宣布了一项新的20亿谢克尔精神卫生计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 02:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-a-two-billion-shekel-supplement-israels-mental-health-budget-will-be-cut/0000018d-0a96-d71c-ad9f-4b963c6a0000</guid></item><item><title>周日，五名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列士兵杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-soldiers-on-sunday-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-0a0e-d8a7-a1df-aebe2edb0000</link><description>自10月7日与哈马斯的战争开始以来，已有300多名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸与以色列安全部队的冲突中丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 23:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-soldiers-on-sunday-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-0a0e-d8a7-a1df-aebe2edb0000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨和艾森科特探索“创造性”人质释放方案；内塔尼亚胡和加兰特坚持军事压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantz-explores-creative-hostage-release-options-netanyahu-insists-on-military-pressure/0000018d-09d7-daa5-a7cf-dff7453b0000</link><description>中间派部长甘茨和艾森科特推动达成协议，释放加沙剩余人质，但内塔尼亚胡和加兰特警告不要在消灭哈马斯之前停火。与此同时，卡塔尔和埃及努力弥合与哈马斯谈判中的分歧</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 22:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantz-explores-creative-hostage-release-options-netanyahu-insists-on-military-pressure/0000018d-09d7-daa5-a7cf-dff7453b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争标志着 100 天。武力不能继续是前进的唯一途径</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-war-marks-100-days-force-cannot-remain-the-only-way-forward/0000018d-09b6-daa5-a7cf-dff659030000</link><description>大多数以色列人相信，军事行动是唯一的出路，任何谈论谈判的巴勒斯坦人都被认为是妄想。需要真正的范式转变</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 21:17:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-war-marks-100-days-force-cannot-remain-the-only-way-forward/0000018d-09b6-daa5-a7cf-dff659030000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯被囚禁100天：以色列人质家属必须发动自己的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-14/ty-article/.highlight/100-days-in-hamas-captivity-israeli-hostages-families-must-wage-their-own-war/0000018d-08c1-daa5-a7cf-dee332850000</link><description>当仍被扣押在加沙的 136 名人质迎来被关押一百天之际，他们的亲属正在考虑必须继续战斗，谁知道他们的困境还要持续多久才能成为公众关注的焦点</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 18:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-14/ty-article/.highlight/100-days-in-hamas-captivity-israeli-hostages-families-must-wage-their-own-war/0000018d-08c1-daa5-a7cf-dee332850000</guid></item><item><title>战争爆发时，我们与这些加沙人进行了交谈。这就是他们所经历的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-talked-with-these-gazans-when-the-war-broke-this-is-where-they-are-now/0000018d-0870-d8a7-a1df-aefef6540000</link><description>《国土报》重新采访了四名加沙人，他们在战争刚开始时就谈到了战争，发现他们流离失所、遭到轰炸，挤在狭小的地区，同时努力寻求医疗救助，并感到死亡即将来临</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-talked-with-these-gazans-when-the-war-broke-this-is-where-they-are-now/0000018d-0870-d8a7-a1df-aefef6540000</guid></item><item><title>真主党导弹杀死以色列妇女及其儿子；以色列国防军击毙三名渗透黎巴嫩边境的恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-missile-kills-two-israelis-idf-kills-terrorists-infiltrating-lebanon-border/0000018d-0859-d8a7-a1df-aeffda470000</link><description>以色列军队称袭击了黎巴嫩真主党目标，并下令关闭边境地区的民用交通。 ■ 以色列国防军估计，渗透边境的恐怖分子计划袭击附近的一个基地；巴勒斯坦组织声称对此事负责</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-missile-kills-two-israelis-idf-kills-terrorists-infiltrating-lebanon-border/0000018d-0859-d8a7-a1df-aeffda470000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的高级盟友和顾问因煽动种族主义而被定罪，恐怖指控被无罪释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/top-ben-gvir-ally-and-adviser-convicted-of-inciting-racism-acquitted-of-terror-charges/0000018d-0841-d71c-ad9f-4bc314350000</link><description>极右翼卡汉主义者本茨·戈普斯坦因针对阿拉伯人的言论而被定罪：“我们内部的敌人是癌症。”他因发表美化 1994 年希伯伦大屠杀的种族主义言论而被无罪释放。判决后他说道：“我为我所说的话感到自豪”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/top-ben-gvir-ally-and-adviser-convicted-of-inciting-racism-acquitted-of-terror-charges/0000018d-0841-d71c-ad9f-4bc314350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名周六在加沙地带战斗中丧生的以色列预备役士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-saturday/0000018d-0879-d71c-ad9f-4bfb1dcb0000</link><description>这名士兵的身份是安杜阿拉姆·卡巴达 (Andualem Kabada)，21 岁，来自南部城市加特 (Kiryat Gat)；军方报告称，另一名士兵在同一事件中受重伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:43:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-saturday/0000018d-0879-d71c-ad9f-4bfb1dcb0000</guid></item><item><title>南非在国际法院传承曼德拉的遗产——也出于政治目的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/at-icj-south-africa-channels-mandelas-legacy-for-its-own-political-purposes/0000018d-0863-d71c-ad9f-4be37c4d0000</link><description>有几个原因可以解释南非为何向国际法院提交针对以色列的请愿书。其中一些涉及内部政治，另一些涉及区域和全球，但表明执政党有选择地利用纳尔逊·曼德拉的教义来分散人们对自身失败的注意力</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/at-icj-south-africa-channels-mandelas-legacy-for-its-own-political-purposes/0000018d-0863-d71c-ad9f-4be37c4d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准新监狱长，违反战时政府协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-to-vote-on-new-prison-chief-violating-wartime-govt-agreement/0000018d-0750-d832-a59d-17f75ef50000</link><description>政府投票并批准了本-格维尔的提议，任命其安全顾问科比·雅科比（Koby Yaakobi）为临时监狱专员。甘茨敦促内阁部长投票反对该提议，任命一位商定的候选人</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 13:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-to-vote-on-new-prison-chief-violating-wartime-govt-agreement/0000018d-0750-d832-a59d-17f75ef50000</guid></item><item><title>德国宣布决定代表以色列介入国际法院案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/germany-announces-decision-to-intervene-on-israels-behalf-in-icj-case/0000018d-0787-dd07-a7df-cfff1f090000</link><description>德国联邦政府发言人加入了越来越多的以色列公众支持者行列，表示对以色列进行种族灭绝的指控“毫无根据”，德国打算在联合国最高法院的主听证会上作为第三方发言</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 11:56:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/germany-announces-decision-to-intervene-on-israels-behalf-in-icj-case/0000018d-0787-dd07-a7df-cfff1f090000</guid></item><item><title>冒雨寒冷，以色列举行24小时人质集会纪念哈马斯袭击100天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-rain-cold-israelis-mark-100-days-since-hamas-attack-with-daylong-rally-for-hostages/0000018d-076e-dd07-a7df-cf7ea6a40000</link><description>在特拉维夫所谓的人质广场，以色列人聚集在一起进行 24 小时的抗议、讨论和祈祷，为仍被关押的 136 人祈祷 — — 并对那些遇难者表示哀悼。早上 6 点 29 分，一名 DJ 播放了 10 月 7 日哈马斯猛攻开始时他在 Tribe of Nova 狂欢节上演奏的曲目</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 11:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-rain-cold-israelis-mark-100-days-since-hamas-attack-with-daylong-rally-for-hostages/0000018d-076e-dd07-a7df-cf7ea6a40000</guid></item><item><title>在华盛顿和纽约，巴勒斯坦人和以色列人和他们的美国支持者一起纪念以色列-哈马斯战争一百天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-and-israelis-their-u-s-supporters-mark-100-days-since-october-7/0000018d-0712-dd94-a9cd-47fe26910000</link><description>在华盛顿，亲巴勒斯坦抗议者批评拜登对以色列-哈马斯战争的政策，加沙人的家人讲述了他们的故事。在纽约市，亲以色列示威者与被释放的以色列人一起呼吁关注仍被扣押在加沙的数十名人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 11:12:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-and-israelis-their-u-s-supporters-mark-100-days-since-october-7/0000018d-0712-dd94-a9cd-47fe26910000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩总理与真主党保持一致：我们的命运与加沙息息相关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/lebanese-pm-toes-line-with-hezbollah-our-fate-tied-to-gaza/0000018d-0497-dd07-a7df-cfff4e0f0000</link><description>阿拉伯外交消息人士告诉《国土报》，要求真主党从边境撤退 40 公里并从南部撤军“缺乏任何操作逻辑”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 03:59:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/lebanese-pm-toes-line-with-hezbollah-our-fate-tied-to-gaza/0000018d-0497-dd07-a7df-cfff4e0f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>